{"tid":94663,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個奇怪問題，醫院可唔可以幫我打自己買嘅藥？","createTime":"2017-01-25T11:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:19:40.000Z","uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8efcbfa16c12ed043ed55a17cdabe08708bf6a2c","tid":94663,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我地係私家診所買左隻藥，但診所竟然唔包打埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻藥香港有註冊，合法的，但太新，公立醫院根本跟唔上<br />\n<br />\n到底可唔可以去睇門診，叫醫生幫打？<br />\n其實只要溝落生理鹽水就打得<br />\n但我地自己點樣搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bf186ad6f35ac334d5b0510251eef931a47c3f","tid":94663,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人做醫院/診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50526860821fc34578144feec5d709539ee321dd","tid":94663,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e14ab93ced8eccb980d9486e4373dfe2bfc705a","tid":94663,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔可以 要自己打"},{"pid":"384108f3c60b28f9aa3bc52ad168c14a5fa66d25","tid":94663,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"唔得，因為有咩事佢地要負責"},{"pid":"f825a3a2d95f6f30832a6ef2b3321358fc91c0be","tid":94663,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"On9 就算註冊左又點？ 唔係自己訂嘅貨點知係咪假野？ 同埋無打開打完你有咩不良反應又瀨係醫生問題點算？醫院更加唔會幫你打咪傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一係搵個藝高人膽大嘅私人醫生 一係返大陸囉你想點都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d811f99726be72d05695031ae09516d84c4e40","tid":94663,"uid":57394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:38:0